        "Name": "Swordsman",
        "Details": "A design that started out flawed due to political maneuvering before the Davion Civil War in 2515. The unit suffered from poor workmanship for its autocannon feed and was burdened by its initial use of primitive armor and an engine too light to properly propel it. This version is the result of tinkering and updating during the civil war updating the tech to standard grade and using the weight savings of that change to increase the weaponry mounted. Final weaponry count include an LRM-5, a Class 5 autocannon, an SRM-4, two medium lasers and a small laser mounted in the head.<br><br>X-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
